{"tid":1281462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7/7 轉守為攻反撃戰開始 - 和理非愛同胞大行動","createTime":"2019-07-03T09:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T11:49:14.000Z","uid":267881,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6ce07519bf0c79784042afd249431f6fff535b7","tid":1281462,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9omN8ny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9omN8ny.jpg&h=17e44d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港令北京惶恐不安 公安部內部文件流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275934</a><br />\n6月份，香港締造兩次逾百萬人大遊行，成功阻擋港府推動「逃犯條例」修訂案。7月1日，又有55萬港人上街抗爭，創造歷史，震撼全球。有評論指出，表面上看似波瀾不驚的北京當局，實際上對香港的抗爭惶恐不安。近日流出的公安部機密文件顯示，公安部要求各地公安廳總動員，嚴防香港局勢蔓延大陸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">星光大道、天星碼頭、廣東道、高鐵站，將香港人訊息帶返全中國！全力貫切敵疲我打，轉守為攻，運用槓桿，借力打力</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276116</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/66066786_10217600048025455_3034710375367966720_o_UQZqv_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F66066786_10217600048025455_3034710375367966720_o_UQZqv_1200x0.png&h=447cba0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2b2WPm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2b2WPm.png&h=979c41d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/03/064938_bd9f843326d1d6d9cc9d369b699d58a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F03%2F064938_bd9f843326d1d6d9cc9d369b699d58a9.png&h=abc9eba6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ace0b3df05ea7d7bb20eab8755782bba0db6913f","tid":1281462,"uid":267881,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:54:03.000Z","msg":"各位内地同胞，<br />\n<br />\n我们是一群来自民间的示威者。万不得已，我们并不想走上以身对抗暴政的路，以占领香港特区政府立法会作为我们谈判的筹码；但满口谎言、满口歪理的政府却无意回应香港人不断走上街的诉求。我们只好以公义、良知、以及对香港、对香港人无穷无尽的爱，去抗衡横蛮的政府。<br />\n<br />\n香港特区政府成立至今22年，政经民生每况愈下。现任特首林郑月娥上台后，情况变本加厉，更漠视民间逾百万民意，推出&ldquo;送中恶法&rdquo;。市民于6月起前仆后继，各尽其力，或和平、或理性、或奋勇、或受伤流血，以一颗热爱香港之心，恳求政府撤回修例，而政府置若罔闻，不谙民情，竟置香港大众于不顾，甚至以民为敌。<br />\n<br />\n现任特区政府已非以港人行先，为使政府聆听港人声音，我等市民不得不进行各种占领，不合作运动、乃至今日占领立法会行动。社会或对我等占领者有所批评，但追本溯源，社会撕裂之诱因为何？民怨每日具增之本源为何？香港何辜？香港人何以被追逼至此？我等港人没有武装，没有暴力，只能以秉持正义于心，无畏无惧，奋勇向正。希望能香港政府能及时回首，重回正轨：<br />\n<br />\n我们占领者，要求政府完成五大诉求：<br />\n<br />\n一、彻底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴动定义<br />\n三、撤销对今为所有反送中抗争者控罪<br />\n四、彻底追究警队滥权情况<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法会，立即实行双真普选<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;反送中运动&rdquo;发展至今，在三位年轻市民殉道。我等未忘忧愤，然心存善念，不愿香港再有为民主、为自由、为公义再添亡魂。希望社会大众团结一致，对抗恶法，对抗暴政，共同守护香港。"},{"pid":"09a43da40f635698f911ca54a76fe0fa5608e6c3","tid":1281462,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:24:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c2c145c4bb40eb248a1aeba3251629beeb201ea","tid":1281462,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:32:20.000Z","msg":"轉貼 好似幾有道理<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14P4tdK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14P4tdK.png&h=f728d7de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1db7379878a748c16811e943630677478601d95","tid":1281462,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:32:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fc69ee3ec689fac1663785f8e5c27401d58ba3e3","tid":1281462,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c2c145c4bb40eb248a1aeba3251629beeb201ea","tid":1281462,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:32:20.000Z","msg":"轉貼 好似幾有道理<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14P4tdK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14P4tdK.png&h=f728d7de&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"但而家個方向就係想針對相關單位，唔影響市民日常"},{"pid":"b9f0025a43408ee9c328c3e5d43a89d4594e0dda","tid":1281462,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:29:01.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"77445c2ed41e923adae4d329953efd62f52c7c3a","tid":1281462,"uid":257409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8bdb4a10812e0c19644709d0b2458daed93b54","tid":1281462,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:36:33.000Z","msg":"如果去要注意「反送中」字眼"},{"pid":"dedb5f8d96bac944a4f06c5f00eaff7491084db4","tid":1281462,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f8bdb4a10812e0c19644709d0b2458daed93b54","tid":1281462,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:36:33.000Z","msg":"如果去要注意「反送中」字眼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"搞手巴打同其他巴打研究緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等佢"},{"pid":"ddfc7c8166955b12e0828ffcaf07dbf4be91a106","tid":1281462,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dedb5f8d96bac944a4f06c5f00eaff7491084db4","tid":1281462,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f8bdb4a10812e0c19644709d0b2458daed93b54","tid":1281462,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:36:33.000Z","msg":"如果去要注意「反送中」字眼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"搞手巴打同其他巴打研究緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:49:14.000Z","msg":"護法治 保民生<br />\n<br />\n用幫港出聲，愛港力個tone實無死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}